    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those prepared for a major project or seeking a parts car. The engine currently runs but has a heavy internal knock and several significant fluid leaks that require immediate attention. The transmission shifts roughly, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This car is sold strictly as-is with no guarantees of roadworthiness.",
