      "id": "sybil_14_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface and mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure uncompromising performance and aesthetic perfection. For the individual seeking a turn-key investment in automotive excellence, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
