    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love, you\u2019ve found it. You really have to see this beauty in person to believe how pristine it is!",
