    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This exemplary specimen features the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, maintaining optimal factory compression with zero forced-induction lag. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp gate engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated Torsen limited-slip differential. Retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and four-piston braking system, this vehicle exhibits impeccable structural rigidity and OEM mechanical integrity. Every component, from the sequential turbo plumbing to the underbody heat shielding, remains in showroom-grade condition, free of thermal fatigue or fluid seepage.",
      "price": 48900.0,
