      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with a high-end ceramic coating, completely free of swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin still carries that new-car aroma; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine with no sun fading or scratches. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. Every button, switch, and feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original manuals, both keys, and a custom car cover. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
